title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Sim Update V - released
description:
Today Asobo released Sim Update V right on time because it was already announced that it would release today. With this release we will probably see a lot of new simmers since with this release it is also available on the Xbox Series X/S.

This update will bring a lot of changed to the GUI and also contains a lot of fixes for issues reported earlier. In addition to this some new aircrafts are available and a new livery is being released to celebrate the availability of the game for the Xbox.
